snippet.title: Moon - PS1 Advertisement (1997)
snippet.description:
(Warning for some rapid flashing near the beginning of the video)


An advertisement for Moon depicting some unusual differences from the final release of the game.


Source: https://twitter.com/hoheto1997/status/1303136035342225408?s=20


Moon is a game developed by Love-de-Lic for the PlayStation 1. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moon:_Remix_RPG_Adventure
